{"type": "article", "id": 29652, "title": "优衣库母公司前三季净利润大跌，Gigi Hadid与奥运冠军拍摄Vogue封面｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-15T02:53:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 70, "name": "财报"}, {"id": 7048, "name": "纽约时装周"}, {"id": 7202, "name": "高管"}, {"id": 23146, "name": "杂志封面"}, {"id": 25091, "name": "奥运"}, {"id": 26955, "name": "开幕式"}, {"id": 30225, "name": "广告支出"}, {"id": 30226, "name": "缩减开支"}, {"id": 681, "name": "Ralph Lauren"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 1802, "name": "Zara"}, {"id": 3340, "name": "Valentino"}, {"id": 4949, "name": "Guess"}, {"id": 5170, "name": "Moncler"}, {"id": 5910, "name": "Stuart Weitzman"}, {"id": 6087, "name": "迅销"}, {"id": 9519, "name": "Thom Browne"}, {"id": 15332, "name": "stampd"}, {"id": 2798, "name": "Gisele Bündchen"}, {"id": 17322, "name": "Gigi Hadid"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 55, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160715104107PqU9n7vwugoJkmB8.jpeg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Coach-names-Valentino-executive-CEO-of-Stuart-Weitzman-business,713806.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Valentino 前高管担任 Stuart Weitzman CEO</b></a>｜Coach 集团于 2015 年收购了奢侈鞋履品牌 Stuart Weitzman ，近日宣布新 CEO 兼董事长将上任，由 Valentino 美国区 CEO Wendy Kahn 担任，9 月 13 日生效，接替 Wayne Kulkin，后者在品牌任职超 25 年，Coach 集团表示 Wanye 将以顾问的身份继续与公司的合作。</p><p><a href=\"http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/2016/07/14/gisele-bundchen-to-host-rio-olympics-opening-ceremony\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Gisele Bundchen 将主持奥运开幕式</b></a>｜据巴西媒体 <i>Extra</i> 报道，世界知名的巴西籍超模 Gisele Bundchen 将以主持人的身份出席本届里约奥运会开幕式，即 8 月 5 日在 Maracana 体育场。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/advertising/laurens-fall-campaign-less-print-exposure-this-fall-10487664/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Ralph Lauren 缩减广告开支</b></a>｜Ralph Lauren 将缩减美国、欧洲地区秋季广告费用支出，包括印刷及数字媒体渠道，继续投放的包括康泰纳仕旗下的<i> Vanity Fair、Vogue、GQ、GQ Style</i>，赫斯特传媒旗下部分杂志、以及《纽约时报》和《华尔街日报》。这一举措是公司削减成本策略的一部分。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/media-news/advertising/hailey-baldwin-guess-gigi-hadid-10489078/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Hailey Baldwin 成 Guess 新大使</b></a>｜19 岁人气超模 Hailey Baldwin，Instagram 主页有 650 万粉丝，日前成为 Guess 新晋品牌大使。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/fast-retailing-sees-9-month-net-profit-drop-46-10489029/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>优衣库母公司前三季度利润大跌 46.4%</b></a>｜优衣库母公司迅销（Fast Retailing ）发布截至 5 月 31 日的第三季度财报。截至 5 月 31 日的前三季度内，净利润暴跌 46.4% 至 710.1 亿日元。这一季度，集团整体收入同比增长 6.2% 至 4229 亿日元，营业利润有 18.6% 的增长至 464 亿日元，但净利润大跌 13% 至 239 亿日元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>超模 Gigi Hadid 首次登上<a href=\"http://www.vogue.com/13455547/gigi-hadid-august-cover-athlete-olympics/\" rel=\"nofollow\">美国版 <i>Vogue </i>封面（八月刊）</a>，与美国十项全能运动员、奥运金牌及世锦赛冠军获得者 Ashton Eaton 一同拍摄：<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715093659KLRziOJcvZjewUXq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.689445\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715093650AFRBvK3IaGmuNiTd.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.684677\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607150936571GMAcYvgp2SXhClb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715093645fPCME3l9VpQtX0JB.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691935\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715093646j5oYCL4DqJtxbicm.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.693548\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715093659qaUyLlgVs1iorAIG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.694901\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715093704w2Dpx7PAs8naK1hH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663366\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>温哥华潮流店铺 Roden Gray 以 Thom Browne 早秋系列<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/7/roden-gray-lookbook-thom-browne-2016-pre-fall-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">拍摄了造型特辑</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715083901L5JzDNuIoH6pvmTQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607150839052zL7CNo1Ut4gWYyH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715083907QnT9YkN6M8hsUIEc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715083908IZ7SQpm4XafKjxtP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715083908SW8C3O4TzoXpywB2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\">夏天最受欢迎的颜色之一就是白色了，Zara 最近发布<a href=\"http://popbee.com/fashion/zara-white/\" rel=\"nofollow\">夏季全白色造型特辑</a>：</p><p class=\"multiple\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715103409PUawteNqXRGWQDnM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715103410RrLYkIwZ5KshtTb9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715103410rO9ilkFdsGxK6t7f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160715103411KAlwrvSELcZfiM92.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607151034111Db0xHfSdgEWY9M6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/mens-spring-collections-20